TextBody:
Hello Shawn,
 
Thank you for contacting Netwrix Technical Support. My name is Frantz, and I will assist you with this issue.
We use Java for Sensitive Data, but it's embedded in the product; it has nothing to do with Java you have installed on your machine.
Uninstalling Java will not affect our product
 
Please let me know if you have any questions.
 
 
Thanks,


Frantz Jean Baptiste
